main event: A civilian reported multiple unidentified objects on the ground in Carmichaels, Pennsylvania in November 1964.
interesting points: The objects were described as penetrating the radar defense system.
The civilian had a 'startling experience' and sent the material to the authorities for examination.
The authorities thanked the civilian for bringing this incident to their attention.
The authorities were interested in the phenomenon and requested any additional comments or replies from the civilian.
The civilian's letter mentioned previous 'sightings' in the area that had occurred at the start of 1964.
sighted object: multiple unidentified objects on the ground
